                  <br>&nbsp; Determine your mode selection:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">INSIDE MUSEUM CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Walk, control menu cursor:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Choose game / Select an exhibited object or a display switch:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Press and hold to speed up movement when walking forward or backward:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Look up:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select the games menu display:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GAME ROOM CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Switch to title screen:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Changes to dipswitch screen, adjust settings for each game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">LOUNGE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Stop:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Exit:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">PAC-MAN CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Moves Pac-Man through maze:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">RALLY-X & NEW RALLY-X CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Moves car through maze:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Creates smoke screen:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X or Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GALAGA CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Moves star fighter left and right:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Shoot:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X or Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BOSCONIAN CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Moves star fighter in eight directions:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Shoot:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X or Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">POLE POSITION CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Steer:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Accelerate:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Brake:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Shifts up:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or L2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Shifts down:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 or R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">TOY POP CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire bullets, open item boxes:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X or Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>
